flowchart TD
    A([Start]) --> B[/Read Input/]
    B --> C{Valid Format?}
    C -->|Yes| D[Parse Data]
    C -->|No| E[Log Error]
    E --> B
    D --> F{Data Complete?}
    F -->|Yes| G[(Save to DB)]
    F -->|No| H[Request Missing Fields]
    H --> B
    G --> I[Send Confirmation]
    I --> J([End])
